data.description: Move in ready with a quick close possible. Home is in great location, walking distance to Winter crest Park, Erlandson Park, Robinson Park and Coon Creek Regional Trail area with beautiful creek views along the walking paths. Home has new dish wash, microwave, stove, fridge, and garbage disposal, new  gas water heater in the last couple years. New vanity in lower level, windows are roughly 8 years old. Walk thru bath in lower level. Fenced back yard.  Just needs a little TLC...Immediate possession!
